snippet.title: Final Project teaser.wmv
snippet.description:
This is my 4th and last Half Life2 sp-mod, with 8 sp-maps, called Final Project.
Before this one i made "LeonHL2_1", "Coastline to Atmosphere" and "Strider Mountain.".
What brings my total of HL2 sp-maps on 42 maps. This Final (HL2) Project doesn't mean that i will stop with (sp-)mapping, it just means i will go on with newer fps games after this final one.
please check my website for all my sp-mappacks and sp-mods;

http://www.leon.triplebit.nl/ 

leon
